{"tid":221292,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日ive last day 我由銅鑼灣喊到返屯門","createTime":"2017-04-28T15:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T06:09:45.000Z","uid":53794,"like":60,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d64f6862c86e045b680e713e193c2d8744ec0c","tid":221292,"uid":53794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"我知我係ive仔係垃圾係廢係應該俾連登仔笑 不過我真係唔知邊度揾個樹洞俾自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由小學開始我就係個啲成日唔講野 無乜朋友嘅人 由細到大放學就返屋企 係屋企就俾老母管住 放假都無地方去 老老實實12年小學中學無幾個真心fd 中學去到派dse成績都係完lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁嘅反應<br />\n<br />\n但係呢兩年真係識咗好多人 個人外向咗好多 有新嘅興趣 係班上面識到幾個好好嘅朋友 然後愈嚟愈多朋友 一齊做project 一齊温書測驗 笑下啲fd 放假就四圍玩 上堂就望住中意嘅人... 我真係覺得呢一年半嘅生活仲有意義過之前12年<br />\n<br />\n然後當我知道一切都會完 一切都會係今日作結 我完全諗唔到自己反應會咁大 我以為會好似中學咁乜事都無 但係啲眼淚連自己都控制唔到 係條街都喊到柒下柒下 上到巴士又繼續柒下柒下 我知道以後唔會再有咁嘅光景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到呢度嘅巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你有耐性聽我呢個廢柴ive仔講埋啲廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bead7a0382d79e5e0c8d998238b318647379ef03","tid":221292,"uid":13032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280018c341bce5cc0e5b773b3ce7db6e80830744","tid":221292,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d3fca550f868c76ac7f15b0d9b39722737312e","tid":221292,"uid":93964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src